rows.label: qst702302_msg0003
rows.name:
...You there. Hiding isn't going to
work, so why don't you come out?

rows.label: qst702302_msg0006
rows.name:
My apologies! I seem to
have lost my way... It's
my first time in Iira.

rows.label: qst702302_msg0007
rows.name:
A lost Superbian soldier... I've
heard that somewhere before.

rows.label: qst702302_msg0008
rows.name:
Could you be Meknes?
Iris's subordinate...?

rows.label: qst702302_msg0009
rows.name:
That's right, I remember now!
Iris-san was very worried about you.

rows.label: qst702302_msg0012
rows.name: I guess I can't fool you...

rows.label: qst702302_msg0013
rows.name:
In that case, I'll just have to
kill you and make my escape...!
